AUDIO: 'All right. Now, let\'s look at this in practice. I\'m going to start locally because if a tool says it\'s built for devs, I want to see Docker before anything else. This was super easy to spin up. I\'m going to clone it from GitHub. I\'m going to CD into the folder'

